        "subject": "LU-5783 o2iblnd: Add Fast Reg memory registration support",
        "message": "LU-5783 o2iblnd: Add Fast Reg memory registration support\n\nFMR is deprecated and it not supported by the mlx5 driver.\nThis patch add memory management extensions support as\nbackup of FMR.\n\nThis patch is back-ported from the following one:\nLustre-commit: f2600449ced3a2f78c4b3e650ff29bb88d1e7e45\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/17606\n\nSigned-off-by: Dmitry Eremin <dmitry.eremin@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I58f01aac3cbef0edc0934d75bcf13888f84beb0d\n"
